# Final Interview Formula

```text
Repeated Work ?
      ↓
Precompute It
      ↓
Store It
      ↓
Reuse It
      ↓
Auxiliary Array
```

This single idea is behind Prefix Sum, Suffix Sum, Difference Array, Product Except Self, Rain Water Trapping, Dynamic Programming preprocessing, and many O(N) interview optimizations.
